snippet.textDisplay:
What a beautiful composition! Simple and melodious yet high on the feel factor. I feel that the transition between the notes brings out the character of the song beautifully. For example, (4:11)"bewafa toh hona zaroori tha" to (4:30)"kya mera haath chodna zaroori tha" to (4:49)the gentle flute humming the main tune of the song.

The voices of Sahir Bagga and Momina suit this ballad oh so perfectly. I am quite impressed with Sahir bhai specially, last time I saw him, he was giving a powerhouse performance in Baazi. The mandolin parts were interesting too, added to the overall experience for me. 

Best in the season so far, from what I have heard! :)
